---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="写作入口" description="Reid's Notes 的共创写作入口。">
  <section class="write-entry section">
    <div class="write-entry__copy">
      <p class="eyebrow">Mobile Writing Room</p>
      <h1 class="display-title">手机写。</h1>
      <p class="write-entry__intro article-serif">
        登录 GitHub 后，用一张表单写文章、上传图片、提交发布。不需要打开代码编辑器。
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="write-entry__actions" aria-label="写作入口">
      <a
        class="write-entry__primary"
        href="https://github.com/ZHUCH-520/ZHUCH-520.github.io/issues/new?template=blog-post.yml"
      >
        用手机写新文章
      </a>
      <a class="write-entry__secondary" href="https://github.com/ZHUCH-520/ZHUCH-520.github.io">
        打开 GitHub 仓库
      </a>
      <a
        class="write-entry__secondary"
        href="https://github.com/ZHUCH-520/ZHUCH-520.github.io/issues?q=is%3Aissue%20%5B%E6%8A%95%E7%A8%BF%5D"
      >
        查看投稿记录
      </a>
    </div>

    <div class="write-entry__notes article-serif">
      <p>手机上填写标题、摘要、分类和正文；图片可以直接从相册上传到正文里。</p>
      <p>提交后，GitHub Actions 会把投稿转成博客文章；发布状态为“发布”时会自动上线。</p>
      <p>只有仓库 owner、member 或 collaborator 的投稿会被发布。其他人即使打开这个入口，也不会写入网站。</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .write-entry {
    min-height: calc(100vh - 156px);
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr) minmax(280px, 360px);
    gap: 64px;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .write-entry__copy {
    display: grid;
    gap: 26px;
  }

  .write-entry__copy .display-title {
    max-width: 620px;
    font-size: clamp(54px, 8vw, 92px);
  }

  .write-entry__intro {
    max-width: 540px;
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--muted);
    font-size: 23px;
    line-height: 1.85;
  }

  .write-entry__actions {
    display: grid;
    gap: 12px;
  }

  .write-entry__actions a {
    min-height: 48px;
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-size: 15px;
  }

  .write-entry__primary {
    background: var(--ink);
    color: var(--paper-strong);
  }

  .write-entry__primary:hover {
    color: var(--paper-strong);
  }

  .write-entry__secondary {
    background: rgba(255, 253, 247, 0.48);
    color: var(--muted);
  }

  .write-entry__notes {
    grid-column: 1 / -1;
    max-width: 720px;
    padding-top: 22px;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
    color: var(--muted);
    font-size: 17px;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .write-entry__notes p {
    margin: 0;
  }

  .write-entry__notes p + p {
    margin-top: 10px;
  }

  .write-entry__notes code {
    font-family: var(--sans);
    font-size: 0.88em;
    color: var(--ink);
  }

  @media (max-width: 820px) {
    .write-entry {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 34px;
      min-height: auto;
      padding-top: 48px;
    }
  }
</style>
